#### ✅ Model Solution for (a)

**Comparison Table (6 parameters):**

| Parameter | SQLite | Firebase RTDB |
|---|---|---|
| Type | RDBMS | NoSQL Document |
| Storage | Local file | Cloud JSON |
| Internet | No | Yes |
| Sync | None | Real-time |
| Query | Full SQL | Limited Firebase queries |
| Cost | Free | Free tier (1 GB) |

**`SQLiteDatabase` Methods:**

1. **`execSQL(String sql)`** — Executes raw SQL like CREATE, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE.
2. **`insert(table, nullColumnHack, ContentValues)`** — Inserts a row, returns row ID.
3. **`query(...)`** — Performs a SELECT and returns a `Cursor`.
4. **`update(table, CV, whereClause, whereArgs)`** — Updates rows, returns affected count.
5. **`delete(table, whereClause, whereArgs)`** — Deletes rows, returns affected count.
6. **`close()`** — Releases database resources.

